   Collection
   Cinema

   This collection is the only one of its kind in Europe, built to honour
   the exceptional but little-known talents of the film industry’s most
   skilled artists. And what better place for it than Lyon, the birthplace
   of cinema?

   Features 1000m² dedicated to cinema, with a guided tour of many
   legendary films from the 1960s to present day.

